T02D3289:33a-1: badzra h'um k'a ra s'a dha nam /
T02D3289:33a-3: rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi sgrub thabs /

T02D3289:33a-6: / yi ge h'um 'bar ba'i 'od dpung bskal pa'i
